@{b}------------------------------------------------------------@{ub}

		      BCDPlay 0.34 (5.8.96)

			by Elmar Plischke

		      The better (beta) CDPlayer

@{b}------------------------------------------------------------@{ub}

@{i} Noch in Arbeit ... @{ui}



		    @{"Introduction" link intro}
		    @{"Installation" link install}
